definition: to transmit/to lead/to guide/to conduct/to direct

to go out/to come out/to occur/to produce/to go beyond/to rise/to put forth/to happen/(used after a verb to indicate an outward direction or a positive result)/classifier for dramas, plays, operas etc

sentences.english: Orthogonality conditions of vibration mode functions for bars are derived.
sentences.chinese: 导出杆的主振型函数之正交性条件。

sentences.english: You can also export the test classes to run in Integration Edition.
sentences.chinese: 您还可以导出测试类以便在集成版中运行它们。

sentences.english: A method of deriving linear model of 3-dimention hydraulic shaking system was presented.
sentences.chinese: 导出了三轴液压振动系统的线性化模型。

sentences.english: They are derived by use of the ratio of the macroscopic kinetic energy density to the magnetic energy density.
sentences.chinese: 它们是利用宏观动能密度对磁能密度的比例导出的。

sentences.english: One or more host names can be derived based on the node name of the system.
sentences.chinese: 可以根据系统的节点名导出一个或多个主机名。

sentences.english: The sum rule of the molecular flexibilities is derived.
sentences.chinese: 导出了分子柔度和规则。

sentences.english: Derived certificate is one is suffixal file with PFX.
sentences.chinese: 导出的证书是一个以PFX为后缀的文件。

sentences.english: The communication fails without the proper import and export definition.
sentences.chinese: 没有恰当的导入和导出定义，通信将失败。

sentences.english: In order to export the sidebar, the main content area is temporarily stretched vertically.
sentences.chinese: 为了导出侧边栏，主体区域现在暂时的使用垂直拉伸。

sentences.english: It seems that no connection to the critical phenomenon of concerned system exists.
sentences.chinese: 但理论关联行为的导出与临界现象似乎没有联系。

sentences.english: Once the data backup is completed, the data can be exported.
sentences.chinese: 完成数据备份之后，可以导出数据。

sentences.english: We had a number of workstations and full-time staff to manually perform the exports.
sentences.chinese: 我们有一些工作站和专职人员来手动地执行导出。

sentences.english: To begin, explore the process you just subscribed to.
sentences.chinese: 开始只导出您想要订阅的流程。

sentences.english: Browse to the source directory where you just saved the exported files.
sentences.chinese: 导航到保存导出文件的源目录。

sentences.english: The formula of the molar heat capacity of Onnes gas in arbitrary quasi-static process is derived.
sentences.chinese: 导出了昂尼斯气体在任意准静过程中的摩尔热容公式。

sentences.english: You can also export images as bitmap files.
sentences.chinese: 此外，还可以以位图文件导出图片。
